Status report of Yi Tong Tse on 4/19/99

  Ported the DPI code to hardware.  Currently it works with clean sources
  (sources with picture boundary aligned with PES headers).

  Used Divicom encoder output for the live feed, and set up Hydrogen
  video server to provide the ad feed.

  Currently only the DPI code runs on Demux DSP and Jinbo's code runs on
  Mux DSP.  The ratemux and clean cut modules have not been integrated yet.

